    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hardware that is used in the construction of buildings and other structures, such as screws, nuts, and bolts, and that is generally meant to be concealed.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
